OL,3,CMaternity services at two Devon
OL,4,Chospitals 'require improvement'
OL,6,FMaternity services at two hospitals in
OL,7,FDevon need to make improvements to the
OL,8,Fway care is provided, inspectors say.
OL,10,FThe Care Quality Commission has rated
OL,11,Fmaternity services at Royal Devon &
OL,12,FExeter (RD&E) Hospital and North Devon
OL,13,FDistrict Hospital (NDDH) as 'requires
OL,14,Fimprovement,' following inspections in
OL,15,FNovember.
OL,17,FThe hospitals, run by Royal Devon
OL,18,FUniversity Healthcare NHS Foundation
OL,19,FTrust, were inspected as part of CQC's
OL,20,Fnational maternity services inspection
OL,21,Fprogramme.
