OL,3,CMaternity services at two Devon
OL,4,Chospitals 'require improvement'
OL,6,FOverall, maternity services at NDDH
OL,7,Fwere re-rated as 'requires
OL,8,Fimprovement'.
OL,10,FThe rating for how well-led they are
OL,11,Fwas downgraded from 'good' to
OL,12,F'requires improvement', while they
OL,13,Fwere re-rated as "'requires
OL,14,Fimprovement' for how safe they are.
OL,16,FIt was the first time maternity
OL,17,Fservices at RDE were rated as a
OL,18,Fstandalone core service. Previously,
OL,19,Fmaternity and gynaecology services
OL,20,Fwere inspected and rated together.
