OL,6,FThe trust which runs both hospitals
OL,7,Fsaid it was "disappointed" with the
OL,8,Freport, and is working to address the
OL,9,Ffindings.
OL,11,FAt Royal Devon & Exeter (RD&E)
OL,12,FHospital, watchdog inspectors found:
OL,14,FCarolyn Jenkinson, CQC's deputy
OL,15,Fdirector of secondary and specialist
OL,16,Fcare said inspectors found staff
OL,17,F"doing their best to provide good care
OL,18,Fin a challenging environment" but
OL,19,F"incidents and risks were being
OL,20,Fmissed."
