OL,6,FShe added staffing levels at the RD&E
OL,7,F"didn't always keep people safe" and
OL,8,Fidentified several incidents which
OL,9,Fmeant people using the service were at
OL,10,Frisk of harm.
OL,12,FAt North Devon District Hospital
OL,13,F(NDDH), watchdog inspectors found:
OL,15,FMs Jenkinson said inspectors
OL,16,Fidentified specific concerns with the
OL,17,FNDDH around triage, incident reporting
OL,18,Fand how leaders were auditing the
OL,19,Fservice, which meant it "relied on
OL,20,Findividual clinical judgement."
