OL,6,FShe added record keeping was "poor" at
OL,7,Fthe NDDH and "details were missing" on
OL,8,Fincident reports which put people at
OL,9,Frisk of harm.
OL,11,FThe Royal Devon University Healthcare
OL,12,FNHS Foundation Trust said it was
OL,13,F"disappointed" with the findings.
OL,15,FSam Higginson, Chief Executive
OL,16,FOfficer, said: "As a learning
OL,17,Forganisation, we use all feedback as
OL,18,Fan opportunity to improve our services
OL,19,Fand work is already underway to
OL,20,Faddress the findings in the report.
